Package: page-the-ripper
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Tensor Lab Research <kai5263499@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: Scan, OCR, and build searchable PDFs from Epson network scanners
 FastAPI service that drives SANE and eSCL scanners, applies image
 cleanup, and produces text-searchable PDFs via OCRmyPDF.
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-venv, python3-dev, sane-utils,
 tesseract-ocr, tesseract-ocr-eng, ghostscript, libxml2-dev, libxslt1-dev,
 libjpeg-dev, zlib1g-dev, libqpdf-dev
Recommends: unpaper, pngquant
Section: utils
Priority: optional
